title: Hulu Xiang Dingdang
synopsis: The story of the animated series "Gourd Jingle Bells" takes place in a residential area of ​​a courtyard house in the city. Although it is surrounded by modern buildings with tall buildings, people living in the courtyard house surrounded by blue bricks and green tiles and trees still enjoy this. A rare comfort. Living here is the knowledgeable old TCM doctor Grandpa Hua, the Bao Hulu boy who has been following Grandpa Hua to learn Chinese medicine and health knowledge, the honest and honest Uncle Hu, the lovely Aunt Hu, the naughty Gang Juner, and the a little savage Xiao Xia. They have very different personalities, just like the neighbors and friends that we usually like to hear and hear, around the common sense of Chinese medicine and Chinese medicine, many fascinating and interesting stories happened to them. The TCM theories contained in each episode of this film range from "Heaven and Man, Yin and Yang and Five Elements" to the application of TCM "cupping and Tuina"; from the use of TCM materials to the introduction of famous ancient Chinese physicians. In the later part of the story, famous medical experts such as Zhang Zhongjing and Li Shizhen will reappear, and they will surely collide with modern people to create infinite sparks. These settings are connected by the image of "Bao Hulu", which makes the whole film cheerful and relaxed, which is also the key embodiment of the entertainment of the whole work. Through these stories, Bao Hulu learned a lot of Chinese medicine knowledge from Grandpa Hua, and helped Bao Hulu understand the evolution and eventually become Dingdang Bao Hulu.  (translated from qq)

title: Ben Ben Yu Jiling Zhi Yishi Xingqiu Xin
synopsis: Stupid Bear and Clever Dog found a strange machine in the tunnel near the town. Due to misoperation, they sent themselves to a strange planet, which is the Five Planets. It turns out that this machine is an instrument made by Xiangxianglang that can travel between stars. According to legend, their Weasel family helped the Five Planets build an underground castle with a huge number of energy coins hidden inside. In order to obtain energy coins, Xiangxianglang tricked the Lone Wolf and the Lost Brother Lan to be their helpers and came to the Five Planets. The five planets once had a high degree of civilization. Due to the excessive development of resources to produce energy coins, the environmental pollution was so serious that the people of the five planets fled their homes one after another. The five planets who temporarily lived on the earth brought the cat Xiaoduoduo to stop Xiangxianglang and them, accidentally saving the dumb and clever. And use energy coins to help...  (translated from youku)

title: Kasite Shenqi Zhi Lu
synopsis: This film is the first cartoon in China to reflect the world natural heritage of Karst. Produced jointly by Guangxi Huanjiang Maonan Autonomous County and Guangxi Millennium Legend Company, this project is a gift to the 30th anniversary of the establishment of Guangxi Huanjiang Maonan Autonomous County, with the "Southern Silk Road" as the main line of the Guizhou and Guizhou Ancient Road, and it is about a Maonan young man Remy travels far to find happiness. With the help of Karst Elves, he fights against the mountain demon brothers in an adventure story. The protagonist Lemi is strong and brave, looking for happiness for the village, wading through the mountains and rivers, passing by the famous natural scenic area of ​​Huanjiang, Guizhou Ancient Road, Niujiaozhai Waterfalls, Mulun National Nature Reserve, Yangmei Pass, Amb Canyon, etc., to show the world's nature around the river The magic and beauty of heritage karst landforms, as well as the harmony between man and nature. The animation allows the audience to feel the charm of Huanjiang's natural scenery through colorful scenes. In the lively and interesting stories, the concept of "green, healthy, and environmental protection" is integrated into the world natural heritage protection, and it is fun to teach and cultivate children's environmental awareness of paying attention to and protecting nature. The film was broadcast on Guangxi and Guangxi Satellite TV in December 2017 and landed on Thailand’s CCTV in June 2018.  (translated from bilibili)

title: Tongge Wawa Zhi Dou Hei Feng Guai
synopsis: The children's song doll has a beautiful hometown destroyed by black wind monsters. Grandpa Idiom tells Tonggehua that as long as he learns 50 idiom songs, he can defeat the black wind monsters and make his hometown beautiful again. When Grandpa Idiom saw that the children's song doll went to fight the black wind monster, he was a little afraid of difficulty, so he brought him into the country of idioms to refine his eyes. At the same time, he took him to the Museum of Chinese Idioms to watch cartoons for education. The children's song doll overcame many difficulties in the idiom country, and finally learned 50 idiom songs, and became glaring eyes. During his struggle with the Black Wind Monster, he discovered that the Black Wind Monster was a typo with the prefix rain. The children's song doll targeted him to defeat him with the word "rain", and finally used the word "show" to make the black wind monster show a fox tail. The children’s song doll suddenly realized that it turned out that the “haze” of the smog was wrongly written as the beginning of the word “rain” and the end of the word “raccoon”, so he became both cunning (the nature of the fox) and fickle (the nature of the rain). Monster-Black Wind Monster. The children's song doll wrote a correct smog word "haze" and threw it at the black wind monster. The black wind monster was exposed and fell to the ground. The hat on his head ("rain") flew up, and the hat became a god bottle of river water. The water from the god bottle rushed down, drowning out the black wind monster, and flowing into the dry river of the orange sweet garden. , The hometown of children's songs and dolls has come back to life.  (translated from youku)

title: Yugongyishan
synopsis: There are two big mountains, Taihang and Wangwu, in the Jishui River Basin. The high mountains are dangerous and it is very inconvenient for people to travel. Yu Gong who lives in Beishan is determined to move away from the mountain to benefit the people. He rejected all the opinions and led the whole family and villagers to dig shoulders and carry the rocks and soil to the shore of the East China Sea. The wise old man living in Hewan laughed at Yugong's dullness, thinking that with the limited energy of Yugong and the villagers, it was impossible to level the two mountains. Yugong believes that as long as you are not afraid of difficulties and persevere in doing things, you will be able to succeed. The mountains will not rise, but the children and grandchildren who are dedicated to digging mountains will pass on from generation to generation, so why not dig the mountains. After the mountain god knew about it, he reported to the Emperor of Heaven. The Emperor of Heaven was moved by Yu Gong's spirit and sent two Hercules to carry the two mountains away. Since then, the people are no longer trapped by dangers, and the spirit of foolishness has been passed down through the ages. (translated from qq)
